OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBahrain jails men over     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FYouTube discussion of Islam
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Three members of a religious and       
OL,6, cultural society in Bahrain that       
OL,7, advocates open discussion of Islamic   
OL,8, issues have been given jail terms.     
OL,10,FThey were prosecuted under a law that  
OL,11,Fcriminalises "ridicule" of any of      
OL,12,FBahrain's recognised religious texts,  
OL,13,Fwhich include the Quran and the Bible. 
OL,15,FHuman rights groups say the men were   
OL,16,Fpersecuted for expressing their right  
OL,17,Fto free speech and belief.             
OL,19,FThe society said the case had fuelled  
OL,20,Fviolence against it members.           
